ygData.messageBody:
Hiyas :) I have seen the aviak's by Lake Rathe, my question is are they good
or evil? I hunt with a ranger who will also let me die if i kill most
animals (the ranger is question is my husband) The aviaks look to me dubious
or indiff so i am unsure. Does anyone know? thx:)
